data.meta_description: Camille Keaton: Camille Keaton. Actress: I Spit on Your Grave. Camille Keaton was born on 20 July 1947 in Pine Bluff, Arkansas, USA. She is an actress, known for I Spit on Your Grave (1978), I Spit on Your Grave: Deja Vu (2019) and Savage Vengance (1993). She was previously married to Sidney Luft and Meir Zarchi.
